    <string name="help_body_1">
        To start a sudoku click on:\n
        \nNEW and choose a level\n
        \nor\n
        \nLOAD to continue your session.
    </string>
    <string name="help_body_2">
        On the top right you can pause or resume the clock.\n
        \nHINT unlocks a random number.\n
        \nCHECK checks for wrong numbers.\n
        \nCLEAN removes all wrong numbers.\n
        \nRESET resets the whole sudoku and the clock.
    </string>
    <string name="help_body_3">
        Click on HIGHSCORE to see your best scores for every level.\n
        \nYou can reset your scores for the currently selected level by tapping RESET on the top right.
    </string>
    <string name="help_body_4">
        Once a week there will be a challenge for you to solve the SUDOKU OF THE WEEK.\n
        \nClick on the little pink button on the home screen to start the challenge.\n
        \nYou need an internet connection to load the new sudoku once a week and to see the average time to solve it.
    </string>
